(44, 26, 13, 23, 24, 23, 23, 'light from heaven, above the brightness of the sun', 'Light and Glory Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of divine light and glory. In Acts, the light from heaven surpasses the sun''s brightness, while Isaiah speaks of the sun being ashamed when the Lord reigns gloriously.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
