(44, 26, 15, 43, 15, 20, 21, 'I am Jesus whom thou persecutest', 'Persecution of Believers', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of persecution faced by followers of Jesus. Acts 26:15 highlights Jesus'' identity as the one being persecuted, while John 15:20-21 warns that believers will also face persecution for His name''s sake.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
